{"tid":1928144,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]没事儿就好似財經台既陳巧文一樣, 行得太前. 行前左一年.","createTime":"2020-03-16T08:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T10:55:47.000Z","uid":70194,"like":34,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f8e7c21f610caef7088cf1e099068730674afeaa","tid":1928144,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:16:01.000Z","msg":"睇返佢既舊Posts, 其實港股一直都未行完熊市 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/159798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/159798</a><br />\n<br />\n我有個圖: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qvUQyRp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqvUQyRp.jpg&h=df8f3c78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018年係没事儿最威水既時間，佢的確係睇中左熊市. 個市由33000點插到24500點。(<span style=\"color: orange;\">橙線</span>) <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住大家以為2019年開首係一個短命既熊二反彈，點知夾返上30000點. 之後又炒返貿易戰同埋去到2019年6月開始既反送中運動。就係依D位，没事儿估唔中熊二既大起大跌，個市係2020年1月完成個平台浪。(<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍線</span>)  <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n武肺發酵，引致全球醫療及金融市場恐慌，擔心經濟衰弱同埋供應鏈斷裂，個市之後就開始進入熊三。(<span style=\"color: pink;\">粉紅線</span>)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論: 總結係人都識得講. 但身處其中你又有冇能力係每個點都預計到之後既走勢? 没事儿懷念你係財經台既付出，如果可以，請你返黎同財經台一眾巴打笑看風雲......."},{"pid":"973e0a01ff15e10b37d4d90b3566cdff52c3c17b","tid":1928144,"uid":22839,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:18:48.000Z","msg":"希望佢數緊銀紙唔得閒出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e607517e6c17d1